OL,3,CPlaque unveiled to commemorate victims
OL,4,Cof hotel bombed in Second World War
OL,6,FA blue plaque has been unveiled to
OL,7,Fcommemorate the dozens of people who
OL,8,Fdied when a hotel was bombed during
OL,9,Fthe Second World War.
OL,11,FThe 70 victims were sheltering in the
OL,12,Fcellar of the Marples Hotel in during
OL,13,Fa German air raid on 12 December 1940,
OL,14,Fwhen a bomb scored a direct hit on the
OL,15,Fhotel.
