OL,6,F"I remember people of my parents'
OL,7,Fgeneration talking in hushed tones
OL,8,Fabout the Marples," he said.
OL,10,F"Even in my generation, all
OL,11,FSheffielders were aware of it, but my
OL,12,Fown children and grandchildren knew
OL,13,Fnothing about this piece of history,
OL,14,Fand I was worried that it would
OL,15,Fgradually fade into obscurity, and I
OL,16,Fjust wanted to help prevent that."
OL,18,FOne spectator at the unveiling, John
OL,19,FHaslam, said his father had had a
OL,20,Fnarrow escape from the disaster.
