OL,6,F"My Dad said to me, 'I was in there
OL,7,Fthe night before, just think yourself
OL,8,Flucky. If I had been in there that
OL,9,Fnight you wouldn't be here'," he said.
OL,11,FThe plaque was unveiled by the Lord
OL,12,FMayor of Sheffield, councillor Colin
OL,13,FRoss.
OL,15,F"Perhaps everybody did know the story
OL,16,Fof the tragedy, but as time goes on
OL,17,Fpeople forget and so that's why it's
OL,18,Fso important to put the blue plaque up
OL,19,Fthere," he said.
